15	 *   Each tick re-reads all non-terminal workflows from SQLite (RC-1: no
16	 *   in-memory cache).  For every item:
17	 *     - pending           → fire deps_satisfied (moves to ready when deps met)
18	 *     - ready             → fire phase_start → bootstrapping | in_progress
